0. READ-ITEM A
1. COMPARE A(1) TO A(2)
   IF GREATER GO TO OPERATION 5
2. COMPARE A(2) TO A(3)
   IF GREATER GO TO OPERATION 5
3. COMPARE A(3) TO A(4)
   IF GREATER GO TO OPERATION 5
4. WRITE-ITEM A
   STOP
5. TRANSFER A(1) TO TEMP
   TRANSFER A(2) TO A(1)
   TRANSFER TEMP TO A(2)
   GO TO OPERATION 1
